      <title>德国皮斯托利斯称俄罗斯泄密是虚假信息战争的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/germany-s-pistorius-says-russian-leak-part-of-disinformation-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国防部长表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京正寻求通过虚假信息活动来分裂乌克兰的盟友，几天前俄罗斯媒体发表了一篇有关德国可能在乌克兰部署远程导弹的泄露谈话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/germany-s-pistorius-says-russian-leak-part-of-disinformation-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院民主党人加大力度呼吁拜登遏制以色列战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/senate-democrats-step-up-calls-for-biden-to-rein-in-israel-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党参议员呼吁总统乔·拜登向以色列施压，要求其在加沙地带停火，理由是最近巴勒斯坦平民在与哈马斯的战争中死亡，他们认为美国对人道主义危机的反应滞后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/senate-democrats-step-up-calls-for-biden-to-rein-in-israel-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞启动欧盟运动抨击马克龙的劳工规则计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/le-pen-kicks-off-eu-campaign-slamming-macron-s-labor-rules-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马琳·勒庞在欧洲议会选举之初就攻击了法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的劳动力市场改革计划，称法国人民将为此付出代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/le-pen-kicks-off-eu-campaign-slamming-macron-s-labor-rules-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 16:30:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普权力游戏后，黑莉对共和党提名承诺表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/haley-casts-doubt-on-gop-nominee-pledge-after-trump-s-power-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼基·黑利表示，她可能会在与总统乔·拜登的选举重赛中拒绝支持唐纳德·特朗普，并表示她认为自己不再受向共和党全国委员会承诺支持该党 2024 年提名人的约束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/haley-casts-doubt-on-gop-nominee-pledge-after-trump-s-power-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦谢里夫第二次面临更加艰巨的任务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/pakistan-s-sharif-faces-an-even-tougher-task-second-time-around</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前，当谢巴兹·谢里夫首次就任巴基斯坦总理时，他必须说服脾气暴躁的联盟和愤怒的公众接受不受欢迎的措施，以挽救国家免于违约。这次情况更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/pakistan-s-sharif-faces-an-even-tougher-task-second-time-around</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:32:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
